                <span id="ctl00_cph1_LangUserControl_ListView1_ctrl6_Label1"><p>A recent article from the BBC noted that a survey conducted by a famous name in the Anti-Virus business has shown that 2015 was a bad year for the security of personal and business data. The reason for last year being such a good year for scammers was that more than 500 million digital identities [&hellip;]</p>
